1. Build the Docker image (ecpe4s/exawind:latest)
$> ./build-docker-image.sh

2. Build the Singularity image (exawind.sif)
$> ./build-singularity-image.sh

3. Run exawind.sif
$> ./exawind.sif

4. Change to the demo directory and execute ./run-all.sh
Exawind Singularity> cd demo
Exawind Singularity> ./run-all.sh
